data.description: Welcome to the Lone Oak Ranch in Sanger, Ca just minutes from Clovis. This unique country oasis is ready for anyone who wants to live outside of the crowded city life. Featuring 2,320 sq ft, 4 bedroom, 3 bath on almost 1 acre, this charming country style home has an abundance of utility both inside and out. Inside is a cozy living room with a wood buring fireplace with insert, a spacious dining room adjacent to the kitchen. There are 3 bedrooms on the main level and one large bedroom with it's own bathroom upstairs. One lower bedroom has an ensuite bathroom and the main bedroom has an ensuite bathroom with tub and shower plus a large walk in closet. A basement can be used for movies or additional storage. Outdoors is a park like setting that includes a shop and drive around access for RV, boat or a possible ADU. Imagine yourself enjoying all this property has to offer and call today for a private tour.
